starterText: New Pizza! Prosciutto & Arugula Pizza. Our all new crust is amazing! Olive oil, garlic, fresh mozzarella, and ricotta topped with prosciutto and caramelized onions. Garnished with fresh arugula and a balsamic reduction. Pair is with a 7258 Blonde Ale

How many places can you enjoy a wonderful Colorado meal paired with a fantastic craft beer served by an incredible staff? Come and enjoy them all at Colorado Mountain Brewery. ü§ó
